headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Mogul
content: There’s just something about that sound. Once you’d heard the deep, low roar of those twin propellers, offset by the high, staccato rattle of your turret man unloading .50-cal justice on just about everything else in the sky, there’s no going back. The Mogul has come to Southern San Andreas, and aerial dominance has never felt so righteous.
